<body>
<div type="letter">
    <pb facs="1063636" n="1r"/>
<opener><dateline><abbr>Patav.</abbr> <date when="1709-10-12">12. <abbr>Oct.</abbr> 1709</date></dateline>
<lb/><salute>Viro Doctissimo
  <lb/><rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-119166895">Nicolao Bernoulli</rs> <abbr>J. U. Cand.</abbr>
  <lb/><rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-119112450">Jacobus Hermannus</rs> <abbr>S. P. D.</abbr></salute></opener>
  <p><lb/><date when="1709-07">Superiori Mense Julio</date> <rs type="letter">epistolium</rs><!-- ToDo: In BIBB erfassen --> ad Te dedi, Vir Doctissime,
    <lb/>quod magno meo dolore cum <rs type="letter">aliis nonnullis</rs><!-- ToDo: In BIBB erfassen --> ad <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-1048628825">Patrem</rs> meum
        <lb/>directis intercidisse intelligo. Nam <rs type="letter">literis</rs> ejus certior factus
      <lb/>de felici successu Disputationis <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> Te conscript<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> de <hi rend="u"><rs type="biblio" key="biblio_ME943KC7">Usu Artis
        <lb/>conjectandi in Jure</rs></hi>, quam summo cum applausu omnium Te
        <lb/>sustinuisse referunt, mihi sane temperare non potui, quin
        <lb/><del/>egregi<add><choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice></add> hoc eruditionis et acuminis specim<add>e</add>n publice edit<add><choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice></add>
        <lb/>animitus Tibi gratularer: quod dum pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>stare satago Deum
        <lb/><abbr>M. O.</abbr> precor ut qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> coepit benedictionis ubertate studiis Tuis
        <lb/>adesse, reliquos conatus Tuos porr<choice><orig><g ref="#ograv">ò</g></orig><reg>o</reg></choice> secundet, ad ejus gloriam,
      <lb/><rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-135542286 pers_DE-588-1089924429">Parentum</rs> solatium et insigne scientiarum incrementum, ut<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice>
        <lb/>Tu deni<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> laudabiliter exantlatorum laborum dignum pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>mi<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>
        <lb/>proxime consequaris.</p>
  <p><lb/>Argumentum <rs type="biblio" key="biblio_ME943KC7">Dissertationis</rs> Tu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> utile, curiosum et novum
        <lb/>est, nullus enim <choice><abbr>JCtorum</abbr><expan>Juris Consultorum</expan></choice> ne per somnium quidem unquam fortasse
        <lb/>cogitasset, res analyticas materiis Juridicis applicari posse, omnes
        <lb/>enim quotquot scio, qui ex professo Matheseos utilitatem in
        <lb/><rs type="keyword">Jure Civili</rs> evincere conati sunt, de Geometria tantum practica
        <lb/>egerunt, quam in divisionibus latifundiorum <add>aliis<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice></add> necessariam esse
        <lb/>ostenderunt. Sed qui <rs type="keyword">Artis Conjectandi</rs> qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> ipsa fere nova est,
        <lb/>usum in materiis <rs type="keyword">Juris</rs> monstraret, repertus est, quod sciam,
    <lb/>nemo; adeo ut <rs type="biblio" key="biblio_ME943KC7">Dissertatio</rs> Tua inter alias pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>rogativas etiam
    <lb/>novitatis grati<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> floreat. Quod ver<choice><orig><g ref="#ograv">ò</g></orig><reg>o</reg></choice> uno ejusdem exemplari <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-1048628825">Patri</rs>
        <lb/>meo tradito, me cohonestatum voluisti gratias ago maximas
        <pb facs="1063637" n="1v"/>
        <lb/>inde<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> benevolum Tuum in me Animum cognosco, quem aliis
        <lb/>etiam occasionibus perspectum mihi reddidisti. De me vicissim
        <lb/>velim Tibi persuadeas, nihil exoptatius mihi accidere posse, quam
        <lb/>ut occasio mihi suppeditetur, ipso opere comprobandi quanti
        faciam eximias dotes Tuas tum etiam amicitiam qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> me
      <lb/>dignaris.
    </p>
  <p><lb/>In his oris nihil in re literari<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> novi habetur, nisi quod <rs type="place" key="place_GEO_3170647">Pisis</rs>
      <lb/><choice><abbr>P.</abbr><expan>Pater</expan></choice> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118937669">Guido Grandus</rs> Monachus Benedictinus Philosophi<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> Pro<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>fessor et Doctus Geometra proxime typis exscribendum tradet
    <lb/><rs type="biblio" key="biblio_RT94S4R8">Tractatum aliquem de Variis infiniti gradibus</rs> in quo, ut <rs type="letter">literis</rs><!-- ToDo: Nachgewiesener Brief in BIBB erfassen -->
    <lb/>suis mihi significavit, respondebit ad <abbr>Cl.</abbr> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-119062372">Varignon</rs> <rs type="biblio" key="bibl_MDEJADS3">schediasma</rs>
    <lb/>quo <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118771167">Wallisii</rs> Plusquam Infinita Spatia nonnullarum Hyper<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>bolarum intra Asymptotas exploduntur et refelluntur in
        <lb/><rs type="biblio">Commentariis <rs type="organisation">Academi<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> Parisin<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs></rs> anni 1706. Egregius
        <lb/>hic Vir variis jam Operibus Geometricis nempe <rs type="biblio">Commentariis</rs><note type="comment">Vermutlich <rs type="biblio" key="bibl_GJ69CTRI">Grandi [1699]</rs></note>
    <lb/>in <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-100673287">Vivianea</rs> <rs type="biblio">Problemata</rs>, <rs type="biblio" key="bibl_E87DDNEH">Demonstrationibus <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118639749">Hugenianor<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice></rs>
      <lb/>Theorematum circa Logarithmicam</rs>, at<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> <rs type="biblio" key="bibl_CFZQXJ3S">Libello de Quadra<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tur<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> Circuli et Hyperbol<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> per series</rs>, inclaruit. Et quanquam
        <lb/>Calculus differentialis ipsi ser<choice><orig><g ref="#ograv">ò</g></orig><reg>o</reg></choice> innotuit, non tamen pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>judicatis
        <lb/>opinionibus obsitam et impeditam habet mentem quo minus
        <lb/>illius pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>stantiam agnoscat, eodem<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> nunc utatur. Nam in aliqua
    <lb/>su<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> <rs type="letter">epistol<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice></rs><!-- zweiter nicht erhaltener Brief von Grandi. ToDo: Nachgewiesener Brief in BIBB erfassen --> ita mihi scribit. <cit><quote><hi rend="u">Ubi <rs type="biblio" key="bibl_6EAMFGYN">Tractatus</rs> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-100814891">Hospitaliani</rs> ope
            <lb/>Analyseos hujus (differentialis) mysteria penetrare c<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>pi, fateor
            <lb/>me pro ludo habuisse qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> tunc temporis operos<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> demonstratio<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ne indigere videbantur.</hi></quote></cit></p>
  <p><lb/>Postremo Te rogatum volo, ut <abbr>Prudentiss.<hi rend="sup">o</hi></abbr> <abbr>Dn.</abbr> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-135542286">Parenti</rs> Tuo, cui felicem
    <lb/><rs type="biblio" key="biblio_ME943KC7">Dissertationis</rs> <add>tu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></add> successum l<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>tus gratulor, cultum meum Deferas. Cum non<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>dum adhuc audiverim <abbr>doctiss.</abbr> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-1089923198">Verzagliam</rs> <rs type="place">Basile<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice></rs> profectum esse, eum
        <lb/>adhuc apud Vos agere suspicor, quod si ita sit, si ipsum officiose <add>meo nomine</add> saluta<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>bis nihil ages quod mihi non sit gratissimum.</p> <closer>Vale et me Ama
          <lb/><dateline>Datum <rs type="place" key="place_GEO-3171728">Patavii</rs> die <date when="1709-10-12">12 <abbr>8bris</abbr> 1709</date>.</dateline>
          <pb facs="1063638" n="2r" type="empty"/>
          <pb facs="1063639" n="2v"/>
<address>
<addrLine>A Monsieur</addrLine>
<addrLine>Monsieur Bernoulli Candidat en Droit</addrLine>
<addrLine>à <hi rend="u">Basle</hi></addrLine>
</address></closer>
  
